          <h1>Moehammad Alvaro Pirata Prayogo</h1>
          <p class="tagline">SysAdmin & Cybersecurity Enthusiast</p>
          <p class="subtitle">SMK Industrial Electronics Engineering | Cisco Certified | Open to Cybersecurity Opportunities</p>
          
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/moehammad-alvaro-pirata-prayogo-842a8834a/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-social">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
