            <li><strong>Cybersecurity:</strong> Network Defense, Ethical Hacking, Security Protocols</li>
            <li><strong>Networking:</strong> Network Infrastructure, Configuration, Troubleshooting</li>
            <li><strong>Sistem:</strong> Linux Administration, System Security</li>
            <li><strong>Teknik:</strong> Industrial Electronics, DIY Projects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stats">
