  </section>
          
        </div>

        <div class="cert-card">
          <div class="cert-icon">🎓</div>
          <h3>SMK Teknik Elektronika Industri</h3>
          <p class="cert-issuer">Vocational High School</p>
          <p class="cert-desc">Specialized training in industrial electronics, including circuit design, troubleshooting, and system implementation.</p>
          <div class="cert-skills">
            <span>Electronics</span>
